<figureCitation box="[670,761,400,421]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="29.[111,146,2059,2080]" captionTargetBox="[112,1449,1045,2033]" captionTargetId="figure-21@29.[112,1449,1045,2033]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="Fig. 23. Frontal margin and merus of left cheliped A, E, Portunus pelagicus (152.9 × 68.0 mm) (ZRC 2007.233); B, F, P. segnis (134.5 × 62.6 mm) (ZRC 2007.226); C, G, P. reticulatus (138.5 × 60.7.0 mm) (ZRC 2007.222); D, H, P. armatus (133.0 × 66.0 mm) (ZRC 2007.229)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5342758" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5342758/files/figure.png" pageId="26" pageNumber="225">Fig. 23H</figureCitation>
); 
<collectingCountry box="[172,260,428,449]" name="Australia" pageId="26" pageNumber="225">Australia</collectingCountry>
................................................................ 
